name: Global Girl Project Christmas Cards
description:
Jacaranda Home is excited to bring you Christmas cards to support a worthy cause. 100% of the proceeds go directly to the Global Girl Organization. 
Christmas is the time for thinking of others, taking care of our communities, and giving. Global Girl Project is launching its first major fundraising campaign and would be so grateful for your support.
The proceeds for our Christmas card campaign will go directly towards such things as paying for airfare for the girls, the Wilderness Adventure Camp, and food and supplies for the girls while they work hard on their individual community projects.

Each pack of cards includes 10 wonderfully designed cards from a volunteer artist from Portugal. Please buy as many packages as you want and share with your friends and family!!! The young women from Xerem, Brazil will be so very thankful for your support!!!! 

The Global Girl Project is focused on and dedicated to working with young women, aged 15 to 20 years, from the developing world, in order to provide them with both educational and life experiences available to young women living in the developed world. This organization recognizes that through exposure to different cultures and life experiences in the US, girls from the developing world will have the opportunity to challenge their own perceived life and educational limitations. Through month long exchanges in the United States, and on-going financial support from host families, these young women will be able to achieve their educational goals for the future. 
http://globalgirlproject.org/
